    <p>This SERVICE is provided by HFT at no cost and is intended for use as is.
    This document informs the app's user about guidelines for collection, use and disclosure of personal data .
    By using this service, you consent to the collection and use of information related to this policy.
    The personal data collected will be used for the provision and improvement of the service.
    Your data will not be passed on to third parties or used in any other way except as described in
    this data protection declaration.</p>

    <h2>Collection and Use of Information</h2>
    <p>In order to use the Service, the HFT may require that you provide us with certain personal
    data, such as access to your contacts, camera and SMS as well as your telephone number.
    The information request is stored on your device and is not collected by HFT in any way or
    passed on to other entities other than the persons You provide access to (by SMS or QR code).</p>

    <h2>Log Information</h2>
    <p>In case of an error in the application, the app will collect data and information on your
    phone called Log Data. This log data will include information such as your device phone number,
    your device IP address, the device name, the version of the operating system, the configuration
    of the application when using the service, the time and date of your use of the service and
    other statistics. This data is used for debugging and error reporting, only. This Personal data
    will not be provided to other entities or released publicly.</p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We value your trust in providing your Personal Information, thus we strive to use best
    practice means of protecting personal information. Nevertheless, other Apps on your phone,
    transmission over the internet or any other access to your storage is not 100% secure and
    reliable and therefore we do not provide any guarantee on the security of this app, any usage
    claims, or any value lost due to its not working properly.</p>

    <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
    <p>These service is not intended for persons under 13 years of age, even though there is no
    reason why it cannot or should not be used by persons under age.
    As a parent or legal guardian and You should know and observe your childs usage of the mobile
    phone and are responsible for any follow-up costs incurred in the context of short message
    transmission (SMS) or release of personal information.</p>

